Privacy Policy

Last Updated: June 07 2026

Overview

Premiere Voice AI ("the Plugin") is an Adobe Premiere Pro extension that generates AI-powered voiceovers from user-provided text and enables voiceover editing directly within Adobe Premiere Pro.

We are committed to protecting your privacy and being transparent about how data is handled.

Information We Process

The Plugin may process the following information:

Text entered by the user for voice generation
Voice generation settings, including voice selection, gender, tone, speed, and pitch
User-specified filenames for generated audio
Metadata associated with generated audio files
Audio files generated through the Plugin
How Information Is Used

Information is used solely to:

Generate voiceover audio
Modify previously generated voiceover clips
Restore settings associated with previously generated voiceovers
Import generated audio into Adobe Premiere Pro
Local Storage

The Plugin may store the following files locally on the user's device:

Generated audio files (.wav)
Metadata files (.json) associated with generated audio

Metadata may include:

Source text
Voice selection
Gender selection
Tone settings
Speed settings
Pitch settings
Filename information
Creation timestamp

These files are stored locally and remain under the user's control.

Data Sharing

The Plugin does not:

Sell user data
Share user data with advertisers
Use user data for marketing purposes
Transfer user data to third parties except as necessary for voice generation services explicitly configured by the user
Analytics and Tracking

The Plugin does not collect analytics, tracking information, advertising identifiers, or behavioral data.

User Control

Users retain full control over:

Generated audio files
Metadata files
Project assets created through the Plugin

Users may delete generated files and metadata at any time using standard operating system file management tools.

Security

Reasonable measures are taken to protect data processed by the Plugin. However, users are responsible for securing their local systems and storage environments.

Changes to This Policy

This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically. Any updates will be reflected by revising the "Last Updated" date above.
